| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2176 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3ae786c7-f2cc-5c2b-ae48-9c5d9531aee5"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
